01:13:19.916 --> 01:13:20.916
Iago!

1035
01:13:26.666 --> 01:13:28.040
A Iittle more.

1036
01:13:31.416 --> 01:13:32.416
Iago!

1037
01:13:33.000 --> 01:13:34.000
Hey!

1038
01:13:34.833 --> 01:13:37.957
How's it going. Iittle niece?

1039
01:13:38.291 --> 01:13:39.749
I thought I wouldn't see you again.

1040
01:13:39.833 --> 01:13:41.415
How did it go with Gran and Grandpa?

1041
01:13:41.500 --> 01:13:42.500
Well...

1042
01:13:45.166 --> 01:13:47.874
- I couldn't make it.
- Yes. I noticed.

1043
01:13:48.500 --> 01:13:50.832
- Why?
- I was with a mate.

1044
01:13:51.458 --> 01:13:54.999
He's amazing. but a party animal.
You'd like him.

1045
01:13:55.625 --> 01:13:57.415
I wanted to introduce you.

1046
01:13:57.500 --> 01:13:58.957
he makes violins.

1047
01:13:59.041 --> 01:14:00.749
- Cool.
- I have one of his.

1048
01:14:00.833 --> 01:14:03.999
- You play the violin?
- I can't play shit. but I have one.

1049
01:14:05.208 --> 01:14:08.249
I forgot my keys. my wallet...

1050
01:14:09.041 --> 01:14:12.165
I didn't forget my head
because it's attached to my neck.

1051
01:14:13.333 --> 01:14:14.832
Can I have some cash?

1052
01:14:14.916 --> 01:14:15.957
Of course.

1053
01:14:19.208 --> 01:14:20.832
You always save me.

1054
01:14:23.458 --> 01:14:24.624
Ignore me.

1055
01:14:24.708 --> 01:14:25.999
How much?

1056
01:14:26.083 --> 01:14:27.499
A couple of euros.

1057
01:14:30.083 --> 01:14:32.582
- Pitu. a drink for my niece.
- No. no.

1058
01:14:32.666 --> 01:14:34.457
How are Gran and Grandpa?

1059
01:14:35.500 --> 01:14:36.624
Well...

1060
01:14:37.666 --> 01:14:39.582
Did they hide Fon?

1061
01:14:40.625 --> 01:14:42.124
When he was sick.

1062
01:14:43.500 --> 01:14:44.874
Who told you that?

1063
01:14:45.375 --> 01:14:46.665
Nuno and Basilio.

1064
01:14:51.083 --> 01:14:52.790
Your grandparents are terrible.

1065
01:14:53.416 --> 01:14:55.332
You've met them now. right?

1066
01:14:56.083 --> 01:15:00.124
It was common before.
Everyone died behind closed doors.

1067
01:15:02.083 --> 01:15:03.249
So...

1068
01:15:03.333 --> 01:15:06.665
I'm not making excuses for them.
but it was common before.

1069
01:15:06.750 --> 01:15:07.790
So...

1070
01:15:10.000 --> 01:15:13.665
Fon never came to Barcelona
because he was hidden?

1071
01:15:14.000 --> 01:15:16.665
If not.
I don't get why I never met him.

1072
01:15:17.166 --> 01:15:18.957
No. love. listen...

1073
01:15:20.875 --> 01:15:24.624
Your grandparents think we got hooked
on heroin on purpose.

1074
01:15:25.083 --> 01:15:26.290
That's not true.

1075
01:15:28.291 --> 01:15:30.915
When horse is in your life.
it rules you.

1076
01:15:31.916 --> 01:15:35.874
It's not that your dad didn't want
to see you or be your dad.

1077
01:15:36.375 --> 01:15:37.749
he just couldn't.

1078
01:15:38.541 --> 01:15:39.665
Do you understand?

1079
01:15:40.125 --> 01:15:42.999
He couldn't be my brother either.
or his parents' son...

1080
01:15:44.500 --> 01:15:45.624
He was hooked.

1081
01:15:47.291 --> 01:15:48.957
He used until his last day.

1082
01:15:51.625 --> 01:15:54.040
- Do you understand that?
- Yes.

1083
01:15:54.125 --> 01:15:57.249
He was hooked.
used until his last day.

1084
01:15:59.416 --> 01:16:00.790
Do you understand that. love?

1085
01:16:01.333 --> 01:16:02.333
Yes.

1086
01:16:03.291 --> 01:16:05.540
- Have a drink.
- I don't want one.

1087
01:16:05.625 --> 01:16:06.749
Give her one.

1088
01:16:06.833 --> 01:16:08.457
- Well. well. well...
- Hi. there.

1089
01:16:08.541 --> 01:16:09.749
