1116
01:23:16.041 --> 01:23:18.665
<i>October 24th. 1983.</i>

1117
01:23:22.333 --> 01:23:25.540
<i>I don't have any plans
oryearnings to return to Barcelona.</i>

1118
01:23:26.375 --> 01:23:28.540
<i>I think what I'd be doing there:</i>

1119
01:23:29.791 --> 01:23:32.207
