1122
01:23:41.208 --> 01:23:42.999
<i>Things are great with Fon.</i>

1123
01:23:50.625 --> 01:23:52.457
<i>Things are going well.</i>

1124
01:23:52.541 --> 01:23:57.082
<i>but I can't help thinking
things start well. then I get tired.</i>

1125
01:23:59.833 --> 01:24:04.832
<i>I guess that's living in the moment.
what will be will be. right?</i>

1126
01:24:12.041 --> 01:24:13.457
Hey!

1127
01:24:16.708 --> 01:24:19.249
They're waiting for you
at the lighthouse!

1128
01:24:20.791 --> 01:24:22.040
Thanks!

1129
01:24:38.541 --> 01:24:40.707
<i>May 15th. 1984.</i>

1130
01:24:43.250 --> 01:24:48.082
<i>The sky has been clear and sunny
and I started the astrology course.</i>

1131
01:24:48.708 --> 01:24:51.290
