to watch some slides</i>

1133
01:25:02.958 --> 01:25:06.082
<i>we made of the new moon
during a party at his place.</i>

1134
01:25:09.125 --> 01:25:11.874
<i>It did us good.
we'd come from a funeral.</i>

1135
01:25:12.833 --> 01:25:15.749
<i>One of Fon's cousins lost control
and died.</i>

1136
01:25:19.750 --> 01:25:21.082
<i>It was shit.</i>

1137
01:25:24.125 --> 01:25:26.540
