<i>It would be amazing
to cross the whole Atlantic</i>

1146
01:26:45.875 --> 01:26:48.374
<i>and reach the sun.
the Caribbean vibe.</i>

1147
01:26:49.250 --> 01:26:50.499
<i>I'd love that.</i>

1148
01:27:37.958 --> 01:27:40.415
<i>January 21st. 1985.</i>

1149
01:27:43.458 --> 01:27:46.790
<i>Maybe it's this sun.
but the Peruvians are happy.</i>

1150
01:27:47.416 --> 01:27:50.707
