1199
01:36:40.458 --> 01:36:42.957
<i>November 28th. 1985.</i>

1200
01:36:45.791 --> 01:36:48.165
<i>I have tonnes of time to write.</i>

1201
01:36:49.250 --> 01:36:50.707
<i>We've been short of money</i>

1202
01:36:50.791 --> 01:36:54.040
<i>since Fon fought with his dad
and stopped working for him.</i>

1203
01:36:54.791 --> 01:36:57.707
<i>I've been working
in a comic shop for a while.</i>

1204
01:36:59.291 --> 01:37:00.582
<i>It's so cool.</i>

1205
01:37:03.458 --> 01:37:05.415
<i>I wrote a Ietterto Mum today.</i>

1206
01:37:06.083 --> 01:37:08.832
<i>I hadn't written to her
for a few days</i>

1207
01:37:08.916 --> 01:37:10.915
<i>and she worries
if she doesn't hear from me.</i>

1208
01:37:11.791 --> 01:37:14.332
<i>I didn't tell her
about Fon's friend's accident.</i>

1209
01:37:14.416 --> 01:37:15.999
<i>She'd worry too much.</i>

1210
01:37:16.083 --> 01:37:17.999
<i>I don't want her worrying about me.</i>

1211
01:37:18.083 --> 01:37:19.832
