<i>June 17th. 1986.</i>

1217
01:38:14.916 --> 01:38:17.290
<i>I'm a real sailor now.</i>

1218
01:38:17.375 --> 01:38:18.749
<i>I'm really strong.</i>

1219
01:38:19.291 --> 01:38:22.249
<i>What with the boat job
and Miguel leaving.</i>

1220
01:38:22.333 --> 01:38:23.665
<i>I had some cravings</i>

1221
01:38:23.750 --> 01:38:25.999
