I stopped completely.</i>

1222
01:38:27.125 --> 01:38:28.499
<i>I'm happy.</i>

1223
01:38:30.666 --> 01:38:33.874
<i>I like the drug.
but I don't want it to control me.</i>

1224
01:38:34.291 --> 01:38:36.082
<i>It happens so easily.</i>

1225
01:38:37.166 --> 01:38:39.415
<i>I don't know...
I'm fine right now.</i>

1226
01:38:39.500 --> 01:38:42.457
