but I can convince him.</i>

1229
01:39:51.500 --> 01:39:54.374
Day 5:
July 20. 2004

1230
01:39:54.458 --> 01:40:01.540
I really like the sea here.

1231
01:40:43.250 --> 01:40:47.290
She was rude.
How could she drop the money there?

1232
01:40:48.541 --> 01:40:52.040
