Can't you understand?

1233
01:40:52.125 --> 01:40:53.249
What then?

1234
01:40:53.333 --> 01:40:56.207
- She wants us all to sign a document.
- It's not complicated.

1235
01:40:56.791 --> 01:40:59.957
The problem is we never talk
in this family. Mum.

1236
01:41:00.041 --> 01:41:03.082
- Fine. We don't talk.
- Not about certain things.

1237
01:41:03.166 --> 01:41:05.374
And why's that?

1238
01:41:05.458 --> 01:41:07.957
Where are you when we need to talk?
And who's here?

1239
01:41:08.041 --> 01:41:09.415
- Where am I?
- Yes.

1240
01:41:09.500 --> 01:41:10.749
- I'm here now.
- Yes. now...

1241
01:41:10.833 --> 01:41:12.832
How many siblings were we?

1242
01:41:12.916 --> 01:41:15.207
- This only hurts you. does it?
- No. no.

1243
01:41:15.291 --> 01:41:17.415
It's more important
that the girl turns up.

1244
01:41:17.500 --> 01:41:19.207
We're not talking about money. we're...

1245
01:41:19.291 --> 01:41:20.291
There she is.

1246
01:41:24.041 --> 01:41:25.041
Marina!

1247
01:41:27.375 --> 01:41:28.375
Are you okay?

1248
01:41:28.833 --> 01:41:29.915
Are you okay?

1249
01:41:30.291 --> 01:41:31.749
- Did something happen?
- No.

1250
01:41:31.833 --> 01:41:34.207
- Are you hurt? Where were you?
- I'm fine.

1251
01:41:34.291 --> 01:41:36.165
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

1252
01:41:36.250 --> 01:41:37.832
Do you want a shower?

1253
01:41:38.500 --> 01:41:39.665
- Yes?
- Yes.

1254
01:42:02.958 --> 01:42:03.999
Right...

1255
01:42:05.708 --> 01:42:07.457
If everybody's here.

1256
01:42:07.541 --> 01:42:08.915
we'll go ahead.

1257
01:42:11.791 --> 01:42:13.665
I'll read the document.

1258
01:42:14.666 --> 01:42:17.457
"We are requesting formal recognition

1259
01:42:17.541 --> 01:42:19.499
of the bloodline of our son

1260
01:42:19.583 --> 01:42:23.415
before you.
the Vigo Civil Registry Office.

1261
01:42:24.083 --> 01:42:27.124
For this purpose.
we declare under oath

1262
01:42:27.208 --> 01:42:28.957
"that our late son..."

1263
01:42:29.416 --> 01:42:30.749
Name. please?

1264
01:42:31.625 --> 01:42:32.874
Alfonso.

1265
01:42:32.958 --> 01:42:34.249
First surname?

1266
01:42:34.708 --> 01:42:36.082
Alfonso Piñeiro.

1267
01:42:36.583 --> 01:42:38.707
- Second surname?
- De Ia Cruz.

1268
01:42:39.291 --> 01:42:40.499
Son of...?

